    "Given the expanding use and evolving nature of SA in public health, a systematic synthesis of current practices, challenges, and outcomes is needed.",
    "Therefore, this review aims to provide a comprehensive overview of the landscape of sentiment analysis applications within the public health domain, focusing on studies published between 2020 and 2025.",
    "Specifically, we seek to address the following research questions:",
    "(RQ1) What are the predominant sentiment analysis methodologies and evaluation metrics currently employed in sentiment analysis in public health research? 2.",
    "(RQ2) What types of data sources are most commonly utilized for sentiment analysis in public health, and what are the primary ethical considerations discussed in relation to this data collection and analysis? 3."
